name: TRIMBEX
description:
Trimbex TRIM Token is developed on Polygon blockchain. Trimbex Token has been created to solve a problems but that problem is more social than financial and that is the problem of cooperating with each other. Trimbex aims to change the world for the better by combining Web3, NFT, Metaverse, GameFi, and other Blockchain Specifications.


Trimbex is an Polygon Token that can be used for it with low gas fees with all the operations needed for the  Ecosystem. To develop a complete sustainable and decentralized NFT, Metaverse, GameFi infrastructure by incorporating modern technology such as VR, AI, and Web3 into our Trimbex Chain and Ecosystem.
